{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":602,"text":"Approximately 30 years ago,"},{"time":2940,"text":"when I was in oncology at the Children's Hospital"},{"time":5633,"text":"in Philadelphia,"},{"time":7022,"text":"a father and a son walked into my office"},{"time":10176,"text":"and they both had their right eye missing,"},{"time":13320,"text":"and as I took the history, it became apparent"},{"time":16131,"text":"that the father and the son had a rare form"},{"time":18900,"text":"of inherited eye tumor, retinoblastoma,"},{"time":22442,"text":"and the father knew that he had passed that fate"},{"time":25556,"text":"on to his son."}]},{"cues":[{"time":27431,"text":"That moment changed my life."},{"time":29843,"text":"It propelled me to go on"},{"time":31747,"text":"and to co-lead a team that discovered"},{"time":35279,"text":"the first cancer susceptibility gene,"},{"time":38476,"text":"and in the intervening decades since then,"},{"time":41197,"text":"there has been literally a seismic shift"},{"time":44617,"text":"in our understanding of what goes on,"},{"time":46643,"text":"what genetic variations are sitting behind"},{"time":49531,"text":"various diseases."},{"time":51090,"text":"In fact, for thousands of human traits,"},{"time":54474,"text":"a molecular basis that's known for that,"},{"time":56692,"text":"and for thousands of people, every day,"},{"time":59987,"text":"there's information that they gain"},{"time":62068,"text":"about the risk of going on to get this disease"},{"time":64510,"text":"or that disease."}]},{"cues":[{"time":66736,"text":"At the same time, if you ask,"},{"time":69041,"text":"\"Has that impacted the efficiency,"},{"time":71748,"text":"how we've been able to develop drugs?\""},{"time":73840,"text":"the answer is not really."},{"time":75622,"text":"If you look at the cost of developing drugs,"},{"time":77952,"text":"how that's done, it basically hasn't budged that."},{"time":81341,"text":"And so it's as if we have the power to diagnose"},{"time":85814,"text":"yet not the power to fully treat."},{"time":88626,"text":"And there are two commonly given reasons"},{"time":91092,"text":"for why that happens."},{"time":92560,"text":"One of them is it's early days."},{"time":96032,"text":"We're just learning the words, the fragments,"},{"time":99622,"text":"the letters in the genetic code."},{"time":101398,"text":"We don't know how to read the sentences."},{"time":103553,"text":"We don't know how to follow the narrative."},{"time":106123,"text":"The other reason given is that"},{"time":108602,"text":"most of those changes are a loss of function,"},{"time":110820,"text":"and it's actually really hard to develop drugs"},{"time":113745,"text":"that restore function."}]},{"cues":[{"time":115660,"text":"But today, I want us to step back"},{"time":117842,"text":"and ask a more fundamental question,"},{"time":119870,"text":"and ask, \"What happens if we're thinking"},{"time":122059,"text":"about this maybe in the wrong context?\""},{"time":124792,"text":"We do a lot of studying of those who are sick"},{"time":127951,"text":"and building up long lists"},{"time":130551,"text":"of altered components."},{"time":133669,"text":"But maybe, if what we're trying to do"},{"time":136068,"text":"is to develop therapies for prevention,"},{"time":139290,"text":"maybe what we should be doing"},{"time":140843,"text":"is studying those who don't get sick."},{"time":143225,"text":"Maybe we should be studying those"},{"time":145572,"text":"that are well."},{"time":147747,"text":"A vast majority of those people"},{"time":149544,"text":"are not necessarily carrying a particular"},{"time":151880,"text":"genetic load or risk factor."},{"time":153816,"text":"They're not going to help us."},{"time":155800,"text":"There are going to be those individuals"},{"time":157399,"text":"who are carrying a potential future risk,"},{"time":160068,"text":"they're going to go on to get some symptom."},{"time":161912,"text":"That's not what we're looking for."},{"time":163700,"text":"What we're asking and looking for is,"},{"time":165548,"text":"are there a very few set of individuals"},{"time":168318,"text":"who are actually walking around"},{"time":171154,"text":"with the risk that normally would cause a disease,"},{"time":175173,"text":"but something in them, something hidden in them"},{"time":178136,"text":"is actually protective"},{"time":179970,"text":"and keeping them from exhibiting those symptoms?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":183145,"text":"If you're going to do a study\nlike that, you can imagine"},{"time":185198,"text":"you'd like to look at lots and lots of people."},{"time":188030,"text":"We'd have to go and have a pretty wide study,"},{"time":191322,"text":"and we realized that actually"},{"time":193057,"text":"one way to think of this is,"},{"time":194586,"text":"let us look at adults who are over 40 years of age,"},{"time":198863,"text":"and let's make sure that we look at those"},{"time":201833,"text":"who were healthy as kids."},{"time":203313,"text":"They might have had individuals in their families"},{"time":205715,"text":"who had had a childhood disease,"},{"time":207527,"text":"but not necessarily."},{"time":209033,"text":"And let's go and then screen those"},{"time":211800,"text":"to find those who are carrying genes"},{"time":213793,"text":"for childhood diseases."}]},{"cues":[{"time":215471,"text":"Now, some of you, I can see you"},{"time":217035,"text":"putting your hands up going, \"Uh, a little odd."},{"time":220330,"text":"What's your evidence"},{"time":221747,"text":"that this could be feasible?\""},{"time":223409,"text":"I want to give you two examples."}]},{"cues":[{"time":225473,"text":"The first comes from San Francisco."},{"time":228421,"text":"It comes from the 1980s and the 1990s,"},{"time":231362,"text":"and you may know the story where"},{"time":233756,"text":"there were individuals who had very high levels"},{"time":236153,"text":"of the virus HIV."},{"time":237421,"text":"They went on to get AIDS."},{"time":239900,"text":"But there was a very small set of individuals"},{"time":242217,"text":"who also had very high levels of HIV."},{"time":245185,"text":"They didn't get AIDS."},{"time":246571,"text":"And astute clinicians tracked that down,"},{"time":249533,"text":"and what they found was\nthey were carrying mutations."},{"time":252920,"text":"Notice, they were carrying mutations from birth"},{"time":256005,"text":"that were protective, that were protecting them"},{"time":258020,"text":"from going on to get AIDS."},{"time":259661,"text":"You may also know that actually a line of therapy"},{"time":262826,"text":"has been coming along based on that fact."},{"time":265946,"text":"Second example, more recent, is elegant work"},{"time":269170,"text":"done by Helen Hobbs,"},{"time":270573,"text":"who said, \"I'm going to look at individuals"},{"time":273235,"text":"who have very high lipid levels,"},{"time":275951,"text":"and I'm going to try to find those people"},{"time":277890,"text":"with high lipid levels"},{"time":279692,"text":"who don't go on to get heart disease.\""},{"time":281860,"text":"And again, what she found was"},{"time":284298,"text":"some of those individuals had mutations"},{"time":286858,"text":"that were protective from birth that kept them,"},{"time":289577,"text":"even though they had high lipid levels,"},{"time":291022,"text":"and you can see this is an interesting way"},{"time":294393,"text":"of thinking about how you could develop"},{"time":296354,"text":"preventive therapies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":298614,"text":"The project that we're working on"},{"time":300558,"text":"is called \"The Resilience Project:"},{"time":303020,"text":"A Search for Unexpected Heroes,\""},{"time":304420,"text":"because what we are interested in doing is saying,"},{"time":306910,"text":"can we find those rare individuals"},{"time":309558,"text":"who might have these hidden protective factors?"},{"time":313883,"text":"And in some ways, think of it as a decoder ring,"},{"time":316863,"text":"a sort of resilience decoder ring"},{"time":318789,"text":"that we're going to try to build."},{"time":320421,"text":"We've realized that we should \ndo this in a systematic way,"},{"time":324270,"text":"so we've said, let's take every single"},{"time":326897,"text":"childhood inherited disease."},{"time":328140,"text":"Let's take them all, and let's\npull them back a little bit"},{"time":330704,"text":"by those that are known to have severe symptoms,"},{"time":333890,"text":"where the parents, the child,"},{"time":335810,"text":"those around them would know"},{"time":336860,"text":"that they'd gotten sick,"},{"time":338190,"text":"and let's go ahead and then frame them again"},{"time":341890,"text":"by those parts of the genes where we know"},{"time":344471,"text":"that there is a particular alteration"},{"time":346978,"text":"that is known to be highly penetrant"},{"time":349776,"text":"to cause that disease."}]},{"cues":[{"time":352430,"text":"Where are we going to look?"},{"time":353658,"text":"Well, we could look locally. That makes sense."},{"time":356146,"text":"But we began to think, maybe we should look"},{"time":358407,"text":"all over the world."},{"time":359858,"text":"Maybe we should look not just here"},{"time":361511,"text":"but in remote places where their might be"},{"time":363471,"text":"a distinct genetic context,"},{"time":366501,"text":"there might be environmental factors"},{"time":368143,"text":"that protect people."},{"time":369525,"text":"And let's look at a million individuals."}]},{"cues":[{"time":373987,"text":"Now the reason why we think it's a good time"},{"time":376957,"text":"to do that now"},{"time":378029,"text":"is, in the last couple of years,"},{"time":379789,"text":"there's been a remarkable plummeting in the cost"},{"time":382377,"text":"to do this type of analysis,"},{"time":384612,"text":"this type of data generation,"},{"time":386351,"text":"to where it actually costs less to do"},{"time":388959,"text":"the data generation and analysis"},{"time":391153,"text":"than it does to do the sample\nprocessing and the collection."},{"time":394337,"text":"The other reason is that in the last five years,"},{"time":398641,"text":"there have been awesome tools,"},{"time":400605,"text":"things about network biology, systems biology,"},{"time":403267,"text":"that have come up that allow us to think"},{"time":405228,"text":"that maybe we could decipher"},{"time":407168,"text":"those positive outliers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":409649,"text":"And as we went around talking to researchers"},{"time":411821,"text":"and institutions"},{"time":413725,"text":"and telling them about our story,"},{"time":415294,"text":"something happened."},{"time":416961,"text":"They started saying, \"This is interesting."},{"time":419190,"text":"I would be glad to join your effort."},{"time":422537,"text":"I would be willing to participate.\""},{"time":424464,"text":"And they didn't say, \"Where's the MTA?\""},{"time":427043,"text":"They didn't say, \"Where is my authorship?\""},{"time":430336,"text":"They didn't say, \"Is this data going \nto be mine? Am I going to own it?\""},{"time":434947,"text":"They basically said, \"Let's work on this"},{"time":437226,"text":"in an open, crowd-sourced, team way"},{"time":440107,"text":"to do this decoding.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":443181,"text":"Six months ago, we locked down"},{"time":445696,"text":"the screening key for this decoder."},{"time":449011,"text":"My co-lead, a brilliant scientist, Eric Schadt"},{"time":453589,"text":"at the Icahn Mount Sinai\nSchool of Medicine in New York,"},{"time":456895,"text":"and his team,"},{"time":458287,"text":"locked in that decoder key ring,"},{"time":461156,"text":"and we began looking for samples,"},{"time":463551,"text":"because what we realized is,"},{"time":465037,"text":"maybe we could just go and look"},{"time":466831,"text":"at some existing samples to\nget some sense of feasibility."},{"time":469917,"text":"Maybe we could take two, three \npercent of the project on,"},{"time":472494,"text":"and see if it was there."},{"time":473911,"text":"And so we started asking people"},{"time":475909,"text":"such as Hakon at the Children's Hospital in Philadelphia."},{"time":479446,"text":"We asked Leif up in Finland."},{"time":481691,"text":"We talked to Anne Wojcicki at 23andMe,"},{"time":485364,"text":"and Wang Jun at BGI,"},{"time":487131,"text":"and again, something remarkable happened."},{"time":489319,"text":"They said, \"Huh,"},{"time":491128,"text":"not only do we have samples,"},{"time":492872,"text":"but often we've analyzed them,"},{"time":495068,"text":"and we would be glad to go into"},{"time":496555,"text":"our anonymized samples"},{"time":497958,"text":"and see if we could find those"},{"time":500020,"text":"that you're looking for.\""},{"time":501183,"text":"And instead of being 20,000 or 30,000,"},{"time":503890,"text":"last month we passed one half million samples"},{"time":507042,"text":"that we've already analyzed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":508947,"text":"So you must be going,"},{"time":510440,"text":"\"Huh, did you find any unexpected heroes?\""},{"time":516065,"text":"And the answer is, we didn't find one or two."},{"time":518648,"text":"We found dozens of these strong candidate"},{"time":521686,"text":"unexpected heroes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":523415,"text":"So we think that the time is now"},{"time":526112,"text":"to launch the beta phase of this project"},{"time":528452,"text":"and actually start getting prospective individuals."},{"time":531569,"text":"Basically all we need is information."},{"time":534740,"text":"We need a swab of DNA"},{"time":536399,"text":"and a willingness to say, \"What's inside me?"},{"time":539804,"text":"I'm willing to be re-contacted.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":543067,"text":"Most of us spend our lives,"},{"time":546858,"text":"when it comes to health and disease,"},{"time":548812,"text":"acting as if we're voyeurs."},{"time":551892,"text":"We delegate the responsibility"},{"time":554229,"text":"for the understanding of our disease,"},{"time":556272,"text":"for the treatment of our disease,"},{"time":558144,"text":"to anointed experts."},{"time":561680,"text":"In order for us to get this project to work,"},{"time":565020,"text":"we need individuals to step up"},{"time":567170,"text":"in a different role and to be engaged,"},{"time":571062,"text":"to realize this dream,"},{"time":573987,"text":"this open crowd-sourced project,"},{"time":577122,"text":"to find those unexpected heroes,"},{"time":580802,"text":"to evolve from the current concepts"},{"time":583462,"text":"of resources and constraints,"},{"time":585796,"text":"to design those preventive therapies,"},{"time":589047,"text":"and to extend it beyond childhood diseases,"},{"time":591820,"text":"to go all the way up to ways"},{"time":593397,"text":"that we could look at Alzheimer's or Parkinson's,"},{"time":597268,"text":"we're going to need us"},{"time":599530,"text":"to be looking inside ourselves and asking,"},{"time":602636,"text":"\"What are our roles?"},{"time":604840,"text":"What are our genes?\""},{"time":606513,"text":"and looking within ourselves for information"},{"time":609298,"text":"we used to say we should go to the outside,"},{"time":611940,"text":"to experts,"},{"time":613148,"text":"and to be willing to share that with others."}]},{"cues":[{"time":617200,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":620758,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}